content.en-US:
We offer our customers a simple and straight-forward online application process for personal loans of up to $50k. You submit your loan application online in just a few minutes; you get approved not long after that and, depending on your loan amount and who your bank account is with, you could receive your funds the same business day. There is no lengthy paperwork to fill out. There is usually no need for any phone calls. You receive your own personal loan dashboard where you can monitor and manage your personal loan details, let us know of any changes to your circumstances, and even make extra repayments if you want to you. Simple, responsible lending of fast cash loans for every customer. That’s MoneyMe.    
### haha ###
[applying for any loans](https://societyone.com.au/personal-loans)    

And now down to the details and why we are one of Australia’s favourite and fastest online lenders. If you’re new to the world of credit and applying for products like our personal loans then there can sometimes be some confusion about exactly how credit products work, what types of personal loans are available, and what kind of information from an individual’s credit report will a responsible credit provider be looking for, and it’s not all bad news on that front. We’ll take you through the facts and figures and hopefully help you confidently understand how a personal loan works, whether quick cash loans are really as fast as they appear to be, and show you our range of credit options so you can find the best type of credit product for you from car loans to our Freestyle line of credit account and more.

heading.en-US: How long do personal loans take to come through?

content.en-US:
MoneyMe is about offering customers fast and tech-friendly applications and approval experiences for our suite of personal loans and credit options. This means that when you apply online with MoneyMe, you access a wholly online process which is completed in just a few minutes. If you’re applying during business hours and you have everything you need ready to hand at the time of your application, then you could receive your approval instantly. Once you have signed your loan contract online then we can even initiate the    

transfer for your new funds immediately. Depending on the time of day and which bank your account is with, you may even have access to your funds within minutes. If not, then funds are usually accessible the next business day.    

Apply online today with MoneyMe for personal loans of up to $50,000 or our Freestyle virtual credit card, available for balances of up to $20,000.

heading.en-US: Can I refinance my personal loan?

content.en-US:
Refinancing is a great way of tying up loose ends and eradicating small and cumbersome debts like high-interest credit cards. When you have a personal loan with MoneyMe, you do have some flexibility to manage your loan how you want to. Through your personal dashboard you can manage and monitor your personal loans, opt for making extra repayments or even paying out your personal loans in full, ahead of    

schedule. There are no early termination fees, so we won’t sting you for being an excellent credit customer. Once you are paying the principal of your personal loan amount and your financial circumstances are flexible enough, you can apply to refinance your loan.

heading.en-US: Can I increase my personal loan amount?

content.en-US:
We love rewarding customers and good credit customers have access to lower fees on future personal loans. Once you have repaid the interest on your personal loan then you can, assuming your    

circumstances permit, apply to refinance your loan amount which may result in increasing it.

heading.en-US: How to get a personal loan

content.en-US:
If you’ve identified an area of your life that could be made a little easier and a little more enjoyable with an express loan then now is the time to work out how to apply for one and get your funds as soon as possible.    

Up until recently, money lenders offering personal loans have needed access to a whole host of paperwork and references, bank statements and payslips. MoneyMe is an online lender. Our application and approval process is clean, simple, fast and often results in access to a same day loan for even large loan amounts like a student loan. It’s low doc, meaning that we don’t need paper copies of anything. We even offer you your loan contract online where you can digitally sign and return it.    

Completing a personal loan comparison is a great way to see what kind of credit is available and for what price. Your personal credit history is    

often the biggest factor in what kind of personal loan amount you will have access to, and what personal loan rates will be offered, but there are other factors which are taken into account too. A lender will also asses your general living expenses. To find out whether your loan is affordable, you can use our personal loan calculator to see how much can I borrow and to check how fortnightly or monthly repayment would affect you current living situation.    

Our online application process takes just a few minutes and will ask you about your current employment, living expenses and other debts you have. We will then ask you for secure access to your online banking account. Don’t freak out. This access is offered as a read-only option. We cannot change or alter your bank account and we cannot give away your banking password or pin because we never see it. Your security is important to us and we use SSL encryption to keep your details safe, just like your online banking app or website will.

heading.en-US: How much can I borrow personal loan?

content.en-US:
How much you can borrow for a personal loan will depend on your current financial commitments and your past financial history. We will take into account the whole story here. In the past, a credit report was likely only to show the poor performance of an individual’s credit history and not what they have been doing to repair or refinance. Now    

we have access to the last 24 months of your transaction history so if you were experiencing financial hardship and have started to make inroads into fixing your situation, that work will be reflected in your credit report and very carefully considered by MoneyMe when it comes to what kind of products and personal loans we can offer you.

Personal loans from credit providers like us are simple and straight forward. A personal loan from someone like a close friend is an agreement that you make for money that you need immediately, and they have to spare, with the promise that you’ll pay them back. A personal loan from an official lender with an Australian Credit Licence works in much the same way, only the loan amount is usually a bit more that you’d borrow from a friend, and you don’t know your bank or lender personally. Because you don’t know them personally and because the cash amount you’re asking for is usually a bit more than a mate can possibly help you out with, the promise that you make to repay these kinds of loans is a bit more formal and comes in the form of a loan contract. There are sometimes fees and charges applied to your loan like an establishment fee, ongoing fees like account keeping fees, and you’re also checked during your approval process based on past loans, debts or services you have taken out which generate something called a credit score.    

Personal loans come in all shapes and sizes. You can get a fast cash advance for money you need right now and you don’t have yet, such as a few days before your regular pay day. You might really want to take advantage of a great offer on a new asset like a car or a boat; put down an important deposit for an upcoming life event, or you might need money for an unexpected emergency situations (we hope that’s not the case but you can rely on us to get you approved for the funds you need fast).    

These kinds of small loan are available from MoneyMe for as little as $2,100. What sort of emergencies would quick mini loans help you out with? You might need quick cash loans for unexpected bills like mechanical works and repairs on your car, or you might need a few extra dollars to move rental properties and to cover your upfront costs like professional movers and your bond amount. Life events happen every day and you don’t always have access to extra cash when you need it. That’s what easy money and our mini loans could be perfect for.    

We are the next generation in credit products like credit cards and personal loans. We want to help you get approved instantly and get access to the funds you need, right when you need them. We offer customers speed and simplicity. We take advantage of the latest secure technology available for instantaneous information and funds transfers. And it’s not just for small personal loans that we can offer you instant approvals and fund transfers.    

For larger purchases like cars, a wedding, renovations, and covering the costs for tuition and school courses, college courses and university degrees, you are going to need more than just a short term loan to buy yourself a little bit of breathing space. Professional development opportunities and career flexibility are prized attributes in twenty-first century living. Access to easy loans like variable rate personal loans ensure you can access the money you need for building your career, and comfortably factor in a tailored monthly repayment schedule that doesn’t strain your living conditions.    

Personal loans are also ways to access more comfortable refinance options as well as for helping to manage bills and debts. It’s easy to start falling behind on your bills and repayments when you have mounting financial commitments. Sometimes things just happen, and you find yourself struggling to stay afloat, catch up or get back in front. Even people with bad credit histories can access personal loans with MoneyMe. Due to changes in the information a credit report now offers lenders, you’re most recent history is also captured to help paint a more comprehensive picture of your financial circumstances. This means that if you have engaged, and maintained, current payment plans to help you manage your listed debt then our team are able to see the real progress you’re making.    

An unsecured personal loan can help you achieve a more comfortable financial position where you repay a single lender one flat repayment every fortnight or every month rather than trying to play catch up with multiple debts and bills, possibly falling even further behind. When you have multiple credit card debt and a few other bills that don’t seem like much month to month, you will often find that over the course of a year or two, the repayments you make can be a lot higher than you might have paid had you chosen a different credit product. Choosing a variable interest unsecured loan option can help give you some breathing space by paying out large unexpected costs like utility bills up front so your cash flow remains unaffected for other living expenses. You can apply for a loan with MoneyMe online and without paperwork for up to $50k, comfortably covering all of your existing debt and converting it into a single stream that you may even be able to redraw on like a virtual credit card.    

If you’re planning a holiday, then you might want to take advantage of possible early-bird sales which usually offer significant discounts for holiday-makers who make the full, upfront payment for their trip at the time of booking. Booking travel early often rewards customers with a whole range of perks.
Download the MONEYME app to apply in minutes and manage your account wherever and whenever you need it.
Unlike other lenders, we look at more than just your credit score. Allowing customers like you to realise your ambitions and create your own opportunities.
From answering calls in seconds to approving loans in minutes. We use technology to provide great outcomes – and we do it really, really fast.
We don’t do paperwork, ATMs or brick and mortar stores. We’re 100% online so we can pass the savings back to you with bank-beating rates. It’s access to money faster, and smarter.

content.en-US:
Get approved for a fast cash advance in Brisbane today and you could have the money you need in your account by close of business. We specialise in offering customers just like you all over Brisbane including the CBD, Fortitude Valley, South Brisbane, Redcliffe, Beenleigh, Sherwood as well as Brisbane City, Ipswich, Logan City, Moreton Bay and Redland City. We’re Australia’s online lender stretching right across the country and offering you a fast approval loans process you can complete and submit online in a matter of minutes.    

#### What is a cash advance loan? ####
A fast cash advance in Brisbane from MoneyMe can come in one of two ways: as one of our small loans with a variable repayment schedule and paid to you as a lump sum cash loan directly into your bank account or via our Freestyle virtual Mastercard®, a revolving line of credit that works just like a credit card but instead of living in your wallet as another piece of plastic, lives on your smartphone instead.    

If you’re interested in any of our personal loans like a quick cash loan from $2,100 to $50,000 then applying online is quick and easy. We have developed an intuitive online software solution which allows us to offer an application form that takes you just minutes to complete and submit, a fast approvals process and even faster loan transfer process.     

When you start your application with us online for any of our quick loans, you’ll be asked for some basic information about your current finances like what you currently earn, how long you’ve been working with your employer, what your living expenses are like such as the amount of rent that you pay or what your mortgage repayments are, as well as other incidental costs like your utility bills, your entertainment costs and your general purchases like groceries and entertainment. Once you’ve completed the form and included a couple of general forms of identification, then you’ll be directed to our secure online portal powered by illion’s bank-level encryption protection. This portal will ask you to log into your online bank account and by doing so you agree to have a 90-day statement from that account forwarded to our loans assessment team. That’s all that we receive – a read-only statement in PDF format and nothing else. We don’t get access to your account or even the ability to see your login credentials.     

We use this statement to verify your application data so that you don’t have to waste time uploading payslips or waiting for us to get in contact with your employer to check your salary and employment details. Once our loans team has reviewed your application, you are sent your loan offer. This offer will detail how much money you have been approved for, what the loan term is and what your repayments are. Our range of short term loans in Brisbane start over a loan term of just 12 months and you can apply for loan amounts starting at $2,100.    

Small loans like our cash advance in Brisbane options can be a fast and effective way of getting your hands on fast money. Your application form takes you just minutes to complete and submit and customers who apply for our range of fast loans in Brisbane usually receive a response from our assessment team within minutes when they apply during our business hours. When you’re happy with the loan offer that we have made you then it’s simply a case of accepting it online with a quick and easy digital signature. As soon as the loans team has received your signed contract then your new funds are transferred immediately. This could mean that you get same day loans in Brisbane by close of business or within 24 hours of submitting your application, depending on who you bank with.    

These kinds of loans are variable loans which means you receive a lump sum cash amount into your account and then your repayments are directly debited for the term of the loan. There is no redraw facility available which means you can’t increase your loan with us while you are still repaying it. The good news is that if you need access to additional funds then you can pay out your loan with us ahead of schedule without getting stung with early termination fees (like other credit providers can charge) and then apply for a new loan instead.     

For more flexible credit options which do allow redraw amounts, you might want to consider the Freestyle online credit card from MoneyMe. It’s the same application process and the same processing time. Funds are available to use as soon as you return your signed contract with us so there’s no waiting by the mailbox for your plastic card to arrive. It won’t because we don’t issue them. The Freestyle account conveniently lives on your smartphone where you can use it in-store wherever tap and go is accepted as well as for quick and easy online shopping.    

If it’s a cash amount that you need straight away, then you also have the ability to transfer a cash advance from your credit account to your own or another person’s bank account instantly. Cash advances from Freestyle come with different interest rates to your purchase rates and there may be other fees incurred for this service. Review the terms and conditions that you received with your approval for more details or feel free to get in contact with our team via phone or live chat online to double-check before you proceed.    

#### Where can I get a fast cash advance loan in Brisbane? ####
Get a fast approval cash advance payday loan online with MoneyMe right now in a matter of minutes. Applications are completely online, and we probably won’t even need to call you. We definitely won’t need to call your employer. Get approved for between $2,100 and $50,000 with loan terms of between 1 year and 5 years online right now.
